sentences: In conclusion, Chair Sach summarized the discussions, which he said should not be considered conclusive, and noted that the Secretariat will prepare a report for SBI-22.
He said that, although the discussion lacked a 'revolutionary spirit,' comments reflected broad agreement that the intergovernmental process needs to be adjusted on a number of levels.
enb_long_title: Tenth Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
